text-decoration: none !important; border-bottom-width: 1px; border-bottom-c=
olor: #000000; border-bottom-style: solid; background-color: #ccc;">death-s=
piral financing</a>.=E2=80=9D</p><p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">Still there i=
s in a loose sense some truth to the argument. If people sustainably want t=
o buy a company=E2=80=99s stock, then that does make its credit better, bec=
ause it really <em>can=C2=A0</em>sell stock to pay off its debt. Of course =
if things change =E2=80=94=C2=A0the factory burns down, it stops making mon=
