positive amount of money and use the money to buy Dollarcoins, so Dollarcoi=
ns will always be worth a dollar.=E2=80=9D There is generally a great deal =
more hand-waving involved than that,[4] but that=E2=80=99s the economic hea=
rt of it.=C2=A0Is this argument appealing? It is wrong, but is it interesti=
ngly wrong?</p><p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">Anyway <a href=3D"https://link.=
